p0002 = "Note that on the Mondays of holy Lent we do not add a Kathisma of the Psalter at the First Hour. On the other days we do, and we make 3 prostrations at each Antiphon. The First Hour being joined to the Morning Office, as has been said above, begins straight away with:"
