p0060 = "And Dismissal. And we process into the Narthex, where the customary prayers are said, and the Catecheses of our venerable Father Theodore the Studite, by the Superior or the Ecclesiarch, as mentioned previously; that is to say on Wednesday and Friday. Then the conclusion and the Dismissal."
